"title": "5524: servants, bad",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5524",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Bad servants are characterised by disobedience, idleness and dishonesty.</p>\n<h2>Characteristics of bad servants</h2>\n<h3>Idleness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:11\">2TH 3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:9\">PRO 18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:24-Matt25:30\">MAT 25:24–25:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:20-Luke19:26\">LUK 19:20–19:26</a></p>\n<h3>Dishonesty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:12\">LUK 16:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:25\">GEN 21:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:2\">LEV 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:20-2Kgs5:25\">2KI 5:20–5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:6\">EPH 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:22\">COL 3:22</a></p>\n<h3>Disloyalty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:24-2Sam19:27\">2SA 19:24–19:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:13\">JHN 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:30\">ACT 27:30</a></p>\n<h3>Quarrelsomeness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:48-Matt24:49\">MAT 24:48–24:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:7\">GEN 13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:20\">GEN 26:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:23-Matt18:30\">MAT 18:23–18:30</a></p>\n<h3>Discontentment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:14\">LUK 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:9-Matt20:15\">MAT 20:9–20:15</a></p>\n<h3>Refusing correction</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:19\">PRO 29:19</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of bad servants</h2>\n<p>Ziba:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:1-2Sam16:4\">2SA 16:1–16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:26-2Sam19:29\">2SA 19:26–19:29</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:39\">1KI 2:39</a> <em>Shimei's slaves</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:9-1Kgs16:10\">1KI 16:9–16:10</a> <em>Zimri</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:19-2Kgs5:27\">2KI 5:19–5:27</a> <em>Gehazi</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:16\">JOB 19:16</a> <em>Job's servants</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:8-Phlm1:16\">PHM 1:8–1:16</a> <em>Onesimus was a bad servant who became good.</em></p>",
